data.description: The Updating has been done so now its time for you to pack and move! Fantastic house next door to Liberty Park and steps to one of the many catch and release ponds in the neighborhood. A few of the recent updates include, Fresh paint, new carpet and hard surface flooring. Kitchen has been updated with white cabinets and granite counter tops, range oven and microwave too! Laundry room has been enclosed into house and is not reflected in tax roll square feet. Split bedrooms with easy flow. Backyard has a covered patio and full sprinkler. Neighborhood has pools, waterslide, basketball court, tennis, work out facility and more. Come and see us today! Looks great and ready for new owners! Agent is owner
